Subject: [PATCH] libbpf: Add "bool skipped" to struct bpf_map
MIME-Version: 1.0
Git-commit: 229fae38d0fc0d6ff58d57cbeb1432da55e58d4f
Patch-mainline: v5.17-rc1
References: bsn#127
